WARNING: USE PYTHON3 WITH THIS PROJECT

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

To run correctly, you can install the requirements with "pip install -r requirements.txt"
To run a demo, just type "python demo.py"

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

The demos:

1. demo_compare_rl_minimax.py
It loads the RL agent from the file "snake.csv" and the Minimax agent, and makes them fight against each other.

2. demo_play_yourself.py
It allows you to play against a trained RL agent "snake.csv" and the Minimax agent.

3. demo_self_learning.py
Launches the demo with an "empty" RL agent and a random agent, and shows how the RL agent learns over the episodes.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

alife_agent.py is the RL agent adapted to the ALife environment.
